[I] Udev rules for game controllers and VR devices

[T] List of devices Steam and SteamVR will want read/write permissions on,
[T] to help downstream distributions create udev rules.

[U] https://github.com/ValveSoftware/steam-devices

[A] ValveSoftware
[M] NoTag <notag@t2sde.org>

[C] extra/tool
[F] CROSS

[L] MIT
[V] 1.0.0.61

[D] d5fd7da0abb81fd2f92f7806bd2ea0daad4cf7d8611cd7c876c1d795 steam-devices-1.0.0.61.tar.gz https://github.com/ValveSoftware/steam-devices/archive/v1.0.0.61/

runmake=
hook_add inmake 5 "install -Dm644 60-steam-input.rules -t $root/lib/udev/rules.d"
hook_add inmake 5 "install -Dm644 60-steam-vr.rules -t $root/lib/udev/rules.d"
